LEGACY watched as the CR chamber ran its scan and then shut down. "It
would appear that the offspring is in stable condition." He said
coldly. "Perhaps Talon should be taken to her chambers to rest."

There was a nod from LORD ELDER, "I will be on the bridge if I am
needed." He turned to leave the room, followed by the FUZORS.

LEO PRIME looked at TUCSON and then at TALON as the door to her CR
chamber was opening. "I have to prepare my ship for its return journey
to Cybertron." He said thoughtfully. He also turned to leave.

The med chamber was quickly emptying out.

(TAG)

- Preston
